      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "GCI for primary QoI (wall shear stress, hemolysis index) below 5% on production mesh.",
      "rationale": "Richardson extrapolation-based GCI computed across three systematically refined meshes. GCI for shear stress 3.2% and for hemolysis index 2.8% on fine production mesh (19.2M elements). Asymptotic convergence ratio 0.98 confirms monotone convergence. Criterion satisfied."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
