      "rationale": "In-vitro test conditions (flow rate ±0.05 L/min, rotational speed ±10 RPM, temperature 37 ± 0.5 °C) documented per ASTM F1841. CFD boundary conditions set to nominal experimental values. Uncertainty in boundary specification propagated via sensitivity analysis; impact on RH index < 4%."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
