      "rationale": "CFD-predicted RH values compared against in-vitro measurements at 5 flow-speed combinations. Maximum deviation 14.7%, mean absolute error 0.08 RH units. All predictions within acceptance band. Systematic over-prediction at low flow rate attributed to secondary recirculation; documented as modelling assumption."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
