      "rationale": "Validation conducted on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry identical to COU device. Operating points span COU flow-speed envelope (2–6 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM). Blood analogue fluid (glycerol-water, matched viscosity) used in vitro; correction factor for non-Newtonian effects documented. Validation domain substantially overlaps COU domain."
    },
