      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published benchmarks for confined rotating flows. Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen et al.) is accepted standard for CFD hemolysis prediction. Formal model form uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2."
